Description:

Sets the #jmapnotifications mailbox to auto-expire messages.

Config changes:

jmap_notifications_expire


Upgrade instructions:

This changes only applies to #jmapnotification mailboxes that
are created after this patch is applied. Installations that
want to enable this change on existing #jmapnotification mailboxes
must set the "/vendor/cmu/cyrus-imapd/expire" mailbox annotation
with value "30d" (or any other expire age).


GitHub issue:

None
